Use the following settings: 

Federated credential scenario:тАпOther issuer 

Issuer:тАпhttps://accounts.google.com 

Subject Identifier If you selectedтАпData ingestionтАпwithтАпFederated credentialsтАпauthentication method, then copy theтАпSubject identifierтАпfrom the Google Console screen when you create Data Store else this field is not required. 

Step 2: Configure Permissions for Crawling SharePoint site 

Go to the API permissions setting for the app registration. Add all the permissions as shown in the following screenshot. Grant admin consent to all the added permissions: 

 

 

SharePoint REST API (Grant full control permission selected sites) 

When the connector is pulling data from SharePoint REST API, we utilize the refresh token provided during setup. 

