This step validates your connector, OAuth configuration, GraphQL query, and agent logic locally before deploying to Vertex AI Agent Engine. 

5.1 Set your GCP project and authenticate locally 

gcloud auth application-default login 

gcloud config set project <PROJECT_ID> 

 

5.2 Run your local test script( python test_local.py) 

This ensures your connector works endtoend. 

A screen shot of a computer 

